      <ul class="bank-guarantees">
        <li>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#009688" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
          <div><strong>Garantie des Dépôts :</strong> Protection réglementaire interbancaire des fonds.</div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#009688" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
          <div><strong>Virement Instantané :</strong> Traitement automatisé des flux sous réserve de validation.</div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#009688" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
